  "title": "BIM Coordinator _ LTA MRT Project",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Work with project team to produce shopdrawings, coordination drawings and as-built drawings on Architectural aspects.</li><li>Maintaining and update the complete set of project drawings.</li><li>Coordinate BIM workflows and ensure adherence to project standards and protocols.</li><li>Manage the creation, integration, and maintenance of 3D BIM models.</li><li>Conduct clash detection and resolve conflicts in collaboration with project teams.</li><li>Facilitate coordination between architects, engineers, contractors, and other stakeholders using BIM tools.</li><li>Organize and lead BIM coordination meetings to address design and construction issues.</li><li>Ensure the accuracy and completeness of BIM models and associated data.</li><li>Conduct regular model audits and implement corrective actions as needed</li><li>Prepare and submit BIM progress reports to project managers and stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree/Diploma in Architecture, Engineering, Construction Management, or a related field</li><li>Proficient in operating BIM software with Auto cad/Revit/Tekla</li><li>Minimum 2-4 years of experience working as BIM Coordinator (Preferably with A1 Main Contractor)</li><li>Strong knowledge of BIM standards and protocols (e.g., Singapore BIM Guide, ISO 19650).</li><li>Excellent communication, organisational, and problem-solving skills.</li></ul><p><br />Suitable candidates please email your cv to sumitra@artemisessg.com</p><p>To view more roles within the Construction & Engineering | Project Management Sector please visit our LinkedIn page @ Artemis Executive Solutions. We thank you for taking the time to apply but due to the high volume of applicants, we regret to inform you that only shortlisted applicants will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>EA Lic. No. 22S1050</strong> | <strong>R1330228</strong></p>",
